snippet.title: Valor: Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Embark on a epic journey through a range of different environments and arenas. Upgrade, personalize and finetune your characters, overcome different challenges and bossfights to prove the single most important thing: your worth as a gladiator.

Wishlist now on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1694310/Valor

Join our Discord:
https://discord.gg/T3gUgpm
